Vendored from https://github.com/axboe/liburing

Upstream project license:
- LGPL-2.1 OR MIT at the project level

This repository vendors only the minimal subset needed by Simple's
io_uring backend. The authoritative license for each vendored file is the
SPDX identifier preserved in that file.

Current subset and SPDX summary:
- include/liburing.h: MIT
- include/liburing/compat.h: MIT
- include/liburing/barrier.h: MIT
- include/liburing/io_uring.h: (GPL-2.0 WITH Linux-syscall-note) OR MIT
- src/queue.c: MIT
- src/register.c: MIT
- src/setup.c: MIT
- src/syscall.c: MIT
- src/syscall.h: MIT

For redistribution with Simple:
- keep the original SPDX identifiers in each vendored file
- ship the repository root LICENSE and THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md files

To update this subset, clone the full liburing repository and copy the
required files while preserving upstream SPDX headers.
